[B]Resource update title[/B]
[CODE]EssentialsMiniReload 1.1.3 - 1.20.6+ release channel update[/CODE]

[B]Update post[/B]
This update moves the 1.20.6+ higher release channel to [CODE]1.1.3-1.20.6-HIGHER-RELEASE[/CODE] and refreshes the project metadata so servers, documentation, and update checks point at the newest build.

[B]Version and metadata updates[/B]
[LIST]
[*]Updated the Maven project version to [CODE]1.1.3-1.20.6-HIGHER-RELEASE[/CODE].
[*]Updated [CODE]versions.json[/CODE] so [CODE]1.20.6-higher-release[/CODE] points to [CODE]1.1.3-1.20.6-HIGHER-RELEASE[/CODE].
[*]Added [CODE]1.1.3-1.20.6-HIGHER-RELEASE[/CODE] to the 1.20.6+ higher release history.
[*]Updated README and SpigotMC description version references to show [CODE]1.1.3-1.20.6-HIGHER-RELEASE[/CODE].
[/LIST]

[B]Compatibility notes[/B]
[LIST]
[*]This release targets the [CODE]1.20.6-HIGHER-RELEASE[/CODE] channel.
[*]This release carries forward the custom message locale, customization, notification, GUI, and bug-fix improvements from 1.1.2.
[*]No commands, permissions, config paths, or dependencies were changed.
[/LIST]

